  "governance_notes": "All children preserve parent's global_vars (none). Data operations cover parent's data needs: CheckExistingBuild, CheckBuildStatus, ListBuilds require builds.read; TriggerBuild requires builds.write; CancelBuild requires builds.read and builds.write. ParseInput and FormatOutput are pure functions with no data operations. No child accesses artifacts store. All children are atomic_operation or pure_function as appropriate."
